description:
Dive into new adventures in Island Tribe 3! Check out the hit game right now!

Having made a wish in front of the Altar of Wishes, the settlers find themselves back at their home island again! The great volcano no longer threatens their well-being, bright future lies ahead and the dream of everlasting peace seems to have come true.
 &lt;a href=&quot;
http://static.realore.com/site/upload/games/213385_90c91c12db7d703f60a8bf8357573929.jpg&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://static.realore.com/site/upload/games/213385_90c91c12db7d703f60a8bf8357573929.jpg&lt;/a&gt;

New life on the home island also brings new feelings along with it. The leader of the settlers falls in love with one of the girls in the tribe and decides to marry her. The wedding should take place in an ancient temple the doors of which are locked. In order to open them, the islanders have to find the pieces of magic runes scattered all around the island. On top of everything the bride gets stolen by an evil shaman.
